name: Meme Elon Doge Floki
public_notice: Meme Elon Doge Floki (MEMELON) has migrated from their older BSC contract to a new one on Polygon. For more information, please view this announcement on Twitter.

description.en:
MEME token from Bitball Ecosystem in honor of Elon.
MEMEs created will be converted into NFTs & Auctioned or rewarded to our community.
Token name is in accordance to everything Elon & his love for Memes + doge Floki.
